######################################
#  Adventuron                        #
######################################

start_at = far_1_tavern

start_theme = my_theme
themes {
   my_theme : theme {
      theme_settings {
         losegame_jingle = on
         success_jingle  = on
         wingame_jingle  = on
         failure_jingle  = off
         font            = daad
         keyboard_click  = on
      
      }
   }
}

######################################
#  On Startup                        #
######################################d
loading_screen = codex_chronicles

on_startup {
   : print_graphic "codex_chronicles" ;
   : play_music "ambient_intro";
   : print "Welcome to Codex Chronicles." ;
   : print "This is a text based adventure game. Type in commands to perform actions, solve puzzles and progress the story.";
   : print "------ \n TIPS \n ------";
   : print "- Type 'HELP' for additional tips for the game";
   : print "- Type 'EXAMINE' followed by an object name to view info on that object.";
   : print "- Type 'INVENTORY' shows you a list of things you are currently carrying.";
   : print "- Type 'SAVE' to save your game.";
   : print "- Type 'LOAD' to load a saved game.";
   : press_any_key ;
   : ask_string question = "Before we begin... What is your name?"  var = "name" ;

}

######################################
#  Strings                           #
######################################

strings {
   name : string "" ;
   teststring : string "" ;


}
######################################
#  Locations                         #
######################################

locations {

   far_1_tavern   : location "" ;
   far_2_tavern   : location "" ;
   outside_tavern : location "" ;
   inside_tavern  : location "" ;
   toilet         : location "" ;
   chamber        : location "" ;
   
}

######################################
#  Connections                       #
######################################

connections {
   from, direction, to = [
     // outside_apothecary, north, road_1,
     // apothecary, north, road_2, 
     // far_1_tavern, north, far_2_tavern, 
     // far_2_tavern, north, outside_tavern, 
     // inside_tavern, enter, chamber, 
   ]
}

######################################
#  Objects                           #
######################################

objects {
   
   painting       : scenery "a haunting painting" ;
   // stools      : scenery "typical bar stools" ;
   cloak_woman    : scenery "a woman in a cloak" at = "inside_tavern" conspicuous = "false" ; 
   bartender      : scenery "the Ancient" ;
   ancient_key    : object "an ancient key" ;
   red_drink      : object "a red concoction" ;
   blue_drink     : object "a blue concoction" ;
   green_drink    : object "a green concoction" ;
   yellow_drink   : object "a yellow concoction" ;
   purple_drink   : object "a purple concoction" ;
   incense        : object "a stick of incense" ;
   candle         : scenery "a burning candle" ;
   table_words    : scenery "legible words seared into the table from the flames" ;
   empty_seat     : scenery "empty seat now that the woman has left" conspicuous = "false" ;
   keyhole_1      : scenery "keyhole on the painting";
   chaos          : scenery "the table of Chaos" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false"  ;
   logic          : scenery "the table of Logic" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false" ;
   order          : scenery "the table of Order" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false" ;
   structure      : scenery "the table of Structure" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false" ;
   mystery        : scenery "the table of Mystery" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false" ;
   guardian       : scenery "a guardian watching over us" at = "chamber" conspicuous = "false" ;
}

######################################
#  On Describe                       #
######################################

on_describe {

   //describe far from tavern
   : if (is_at "far_1_tavern") {
      : play_music sound="ambient_night"; 
      : print "You open your eyes." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "The surrounding looks unfamiliar." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "It's night time." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "The air is curiously still and fills your mouth with a stale taste."; 
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "Itâ€™s too quiet, and not a single creature of the night stirs. The only thing breaking the silence is the incessant ringing in your ears..." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "\"What happened? Where is this place?\"" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "Darkness seeps out of the night." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "You can see nothing... except a faint glow to the north." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "Looks like you have no choice but to walk towards it." ;
      : press_any_key ;
   }
      
   //describe far from tavern
   : if (is_at "far_2_tavern") {
      : print "You are getting closer to the glow.";
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "You can make out an outline of a building of some sort." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "You sigh with relief... At least there is civilisation here. Better keep walking." ;
   }  
      
   //describe outside tavern
   : if (is_at "outside_tavern") {
      : print "You are standing at the foot of a strange building which looks like...an apothecarium?" ;
   }
   
   //describe inside tavern
   
   : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : if (is_first_enter_taver == false) {
       : print "You look around and start to wonder what kind of room you are even in.";
       : press_any_key ;
       : print "To your left, you notice a PAINTING hanging on the wall.";
       : press_any_key ;
       : print "To your right, a counter. A narrow door at the back that probably leads to the LAVATORY.";
       : press_any_key ;
       : print "A WOMAN in a cloak is sitting at the counter. She is drinking a shimmering elixer."; 
       : press_any_key ;
       : print "There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the counter. The whole place is strewn with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and mysterious things you cannot name.";  
       : set_boolean var = "is_first_enter_taver"  value = "true" ;
       : done ;

      
   }
      : if (is_present "cloak_woman") {
         : print "You look around and start to wonder what kind of room you are even in. To your left, you notice a PAINTING hanging on the wall. To your right, a counter. A narrow door at the back that probably leads to the LAVATORY.";
         : print "A WOMAN in a cloak is sitting at the counter. She is drinking a shimmering elixer. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the counter. The whole place is strewn with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and mysterious things you cannot name.";
      }

      : if (is_present "empty_seat") {
         : if (is_chamber_open == true) {
            : print "An entire CHAMBER was hidden behind the painting!" ;
            : set_graphic graphic = "opening_chamber"  target = "inside_tavern" ;
            : play_music sound="ambient_chant";
            : print "There is a PAINTING hanging on the wall. A narrow door at the back probably leads to the LAVATORY. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the counter. The place is strewn with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and mysterious things you cannot name.";
         : done ;
         }
         : if (is_chamber_open == false && is_heard_something == false) {
            : print "There is a PAINTING hanging on the wall. A narrow door at the back probably leads to the LAVATORY. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the counter. The place is strewn with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and mysterious things you cannot name.";
         }
         : if (is_chamber_open == false && is_heard_something == true) {
            : print "There is chanting coming from the PAINTING?.\n A narrow door at the back probably leads to the LAVATORY. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the counter. The place is strewn with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and mysterious things you cannot name.";
         }
         : if (entered_toilet == 0) {
            : if (is_chamber_open == false) {
               : set_graphic graphic = "no_table_no_woman1"  target = "inside_tavern" immediate = "true" ;
            }
         }   
         : else {
            : set_graphic graphic = "table_no_woman1"  target = "inside_tavern" immediate = "true" ;
         }
      }

      : if (entered_toilet > 0 && has_not_created "table_words" ) {
         : print "...You notice a small TABLE under the painting with something on it. Was that there before?..."; 
         : if (is_present "empty_seat") {
            : set_graphic graphic = "table_no_woman1"  target = "inside_tavern" immediate = "true" ;  
         }
         // : if (!is_present "empty_seat") {
         : else {
            : set_graphic graphic = "table_and_woman1"  target = "inside_tavern" immediate = "true" ;  
         }
      }
   }

   //describe inside toilet
   : if (is_at "toilet") {
      : if (is_exists "incense" || is_exists "candle") {
         : print "A regular lavatory. Complete with a WASHBASIN, TOILET, and lots of SCRIBBLING on the wall.";
         : if (is_stand_toilet == true) {
            : print "You are standing on the toilet seat, hoping it doesn't collapse." ;
         }
      }
      : else {
         : print "A regular lavatory. Complete with a WASHBASIN, TOILET, lots of SCRIBBLING on the wall and...what's all that JUNK on the shelf?";
         : if (is_stand_toilet == true) {
            : print "You are standing on the toilet seat, hoping it doesn't collapse." ;
         }
      }
   }

   //dweling chamber
	: if (is_at "chamber") {
      : if (!is_chamber_quest) {
         : print "You enter the chamber. The sounds are soothing to your ears and the lingering smoke of burned incense fills your nostrils. Moonlight shines ominously into the room." ;
      }
      : print "Your eyes gaze upon five TABLES in the middle of the room, each boldly displaying a unique colour and insignia - CHAOS red, LOGIC blue, ORDER yellow, STRUCTURE green, and MYSTERY purple." ;
      : if (!is_chamber_quest) {
         : print "You spot a another robed Templar at the back of the room keeping watch. Is that a GUARDIAN?" ;
      } 
      : else {
         : print "You wonder which table has the impostor.";  
      }
      : play_music sound="ambient_chant";
	}
}

######################################
#  Booleans                          
######################################

booleans {
   is_key_exists        : boolean;
   is_intro_done        : boolean;
   is_incense_there     : boolean;
   is_quest_started     : boolean;
   is_woman_ready       : boolean;
   is_woman_intro_done  : boolean;
   emoji_react_picked   : boolean;
   is_woman_helped      : boolean;
   is_heard_something   : boolean;
   is_chamber_open      : boolean;
   is_clean             : boolean;
   is_chamber_quest     : boolean;
   is_asked_work        : boolean;
   is_asked_future      : boolean;
   is_stand_toilet      : boolean;
   is_first_enter_taver : boolean;
   
}



######################################
#  Integers                          #
######################################

integers {
   question_1     : integer "0";
   drinking       : integer "0";
   drink_count    : integer "0";
   toilet_writing : integer "0";
   entered_toilet : integer "0";
   quest_counter  : integer "0";
   impostor_try   : integer "3";
   
   test1 : integer "0" ;
   test2 : integer "0" ;
   
}



######################################
#  Barriers                          #
######################################

barriers {
   chamber : block {
      location = chamber
      block_when_not = is_chamber_open
   }
}

######################################
#  Subroutines                       #
######################################

subroutines {
   //pre game over text
   pre_end_game : subroutine {
      : clear_screen ;
      : print "You are lost outside.";
      : pause "2000" ;
      : print "The night goes cold." ;
      : pause "2000" ;
      : print "Your hands start to shiver." ;
      : pause "2000" ;
      : print "Your mind begins to fade." ;
      : pause "2000" ;
   }


	//game over
   end_game : subroutine {
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : print_graphic "game_over" ;
      : failure ;
      : lose_game;
	}

 	//game over at impostor       
 	end_game2 : subroutine {
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : print_graphic "game_over" ;
      : failure ;
      : lose_game;
	}

   // make right choice
   woman_correct_choice : subroutine {
      : print "<\"Wow... it was that simple... I will try that right away!\"<6>>" ;
      : print "She thanks you one last time and leaves." ;
      : print "You wonder how you knew all this...You hope you told her the right thing." ;
      : success ;
      : destroy "cloak_woman" ;
   }

	//woman questions
   woman_questions : subroutine {
      : if (emoji_react_picked) {
         : gosub "emoji_answer";
      }
      : else {
         : add_choice "You need to send your feet pictures to the devs."  {
            : print "<\"I have... I sent them to someone named \"LUCIFER\"... *sniff*\"<6>>" ;
            : press_any_key ;
            : print "<\"A-and... now... my feet are all over feetfinder.com! Waaaaaah!\" <6>>" ;
            : print "You quickly retreat. Maybe rethink your answer?";
         }
         
         : add_choice "You need to verify yourself in voice chat."  {
            : print "The woman scowled." ;
            : print "<\"Are you kidding me? I was in there for ages. I sang \"Barbie Girl\" in 2 languages. I chanted their shit posts. Even after all that, they told me this is not the way to get verified!\"<6>>" ;
            : print "You quickly retreat. Maybe rethink your answer?";
         }
         
         : add_choice "You just need to react with an emoji."  {
            : set_true "emoji_react_picked";
            : gosub "emoji_answer"; 
         }
         : choose "You ponder her words for a moment, and respond with..." ; 
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
         : done ;
      }
   }

   emoji_answer : subroutine {
      : clear_screen ;
      : print_graphic ;
      : print "The woman turned away with a pensive look." ;
      : print "<\"What? That's the first I've heard of this. React where?\"<6>>" ;
      : add_choice "On the announcements channel."  {
         : print "The woman shakes her head." ;
         : print "<Liar. I've seen many reactions on that channel. I've even clicked on every reaction! None of them worked!<6>>" ;
      }
      
      : add_choice "On one of the pinned messages in the verification channel."  {
         : print "The woman once again turned to you, her eyebrows raised in surprise." ;
         : print "<\"Oh! I didn't think to check the pinned messages. Which emoji do I use?\"<6>>" ;

         : add_choice "The thumbs up emoji." {
            : gosub "woman_correct_choice" ;
         }
         : add_choice "The sun emoji." {
            : gosub "woman_correct_choice" ;
         }
         : add_choice "The fire emoji."  {
            : gosub "woman_correct_choice" ;
         }

         : choose "You ponder her words for a moment, and respond with..." ;
         : create "empty_seat";
         : increment "quest_counter" ;      
      }
         
      : add_choice "On the voice-verify channel."  {
         : print "The woman gives you a confused look." ;
         : print "<\"I'm starting to wonder if you know what you are talking about. You can't use emojis in voice channels...\"<6>>" ;
      }
      : choose "You ponder her words for a moment, and respond with..." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
   }

   who_is_woman : subroutine {
      : if (!is_woman_ready) {
         : clear_screen ;
         : print_graphic ;
         : print "You ask the Ancient, \"Who is that woman?\"";
         : print "<\"Ahh... Don't mind her.\"<4>>" ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : print "<\"She's still stuck on the Opening Ceremony. Unlike most Templars, she never made it through.\"<4>>";
         : press_any_key ;
         : print "<I've told her the O.C. is over and that all doors are open to her now, but I just can't get through to her.\"<4>>";
         : press_any_key ;
         : print "<Sigh... What can you do...\"<4>>" ;
         : set_boolean var = "is_woman_ready"  value = "true" ;
      }
      : else {
         : if (is_woman_helped) {
            : print "<\"Thank you for guiding her.\"<4>>";
         }
         : else {
            : print "<\"A lost soul. Maybe you could talk to her for me?\"<4>>" ;
         }
      }
   }

   //first man question
   man_question1 : subroutine {
      : clear_screen ;
      : print_graphic ;
      : add_choice "Where am I?"  {
         : print "<\"Why, this here is where all newcomers like yourself start off! It's both a starting point and a halfway house, if you will.\"<4>>" ;
         : set_integer var = "question_1"  value = "1" ;
      }
      
      : add_choice "Why am I here?"  {
         : print "<\"That, my friend, is a question you will need to figure out yourself!\"<4>>" ;
      }
      
      : if (is_present "cloak_woman") {
         : add_choice "Who is that woman?" {
            : gosub "who_is_woman";
         }
      }
      
      : add_choice "I have no more questions for now."  {
         : print "<\"You take care then.\"<4>>" ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
         : done ;
      }
      : choose "<\"So, what will it be <4>>{name}<?\"<4>>" ;
      : press_any_key ;
   }

######################################
#  On Tick                           #
######################################

on_tick {

   //outside tavern
   : if (is_at "far_1_tavern") {      
      : if (linger() == 0) {
         : play_music sound="ambient_night";
      }
   }
         


   //apothecarium 
   : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : if (quest_counter == 3) {
            : if (linger() == 0) {
            : play_music sound="ambient_chant";
            }
         }
         : if (quest_counter !=3) {
            : if (linger() == 0) {
               : play_music sound="ambient_apothecarium";
            }
         }
      }

   //if too long far_tavern
   : if (is_at "far_1_tavern" || is_at "far_2_tavern" ) {
      : if (linger() == 3) {
         : print "Struggling? Type \"HELP\" to get some additional tips" ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 5) {
         : print "It's too dark to do anything else out here... Maybe you should head north towards the glow." ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 6) {
         : print "Stay out here too much longer and you will freeze to death. WALK NORTH." ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 8) {
         : gosub "pre_end_game";
         : gosub "end_game";
         : failure ;
      }
   }

   //if too long outside_tavern
   : if (is_at "outside_tavern") {
      : if (linger() == 3) {
         : print "Still struggling? Type \"HELP\" to get some additional tips" ;
      }

      : if (linger() == 5) {
         : print "It's too dark to do anything else out here... Maybe you should go inside." ;
      }

      : if (linger() == 8) {
         : print "Stay out here too much longer and you will freeze to death. GO INSIDE already." ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 10) {
         : gosub "pre_end_game";
         : print "Perhaps this is for the best. Afterall, a templar who is afraid to GO INSIDE the building is not worthy of the rewards within." ;
         : gosub "end_game" ;
         : failure ;
      }
   }

   //quests completed
   : if (quest_counter == 3 && is_heard_something == false) {
      : play_music sound="ambient_gong";
      : print "You hear something..." ;
      : pause "5000" ;
      : pause "4000" ;
      : print "Three gongs..." ;
      : play_music sound="ambient_chant";
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "And... Chanting? Sounds like it's coming from near the painting." ;
      : set_boolean var = "is_heard_something"  value = "true" ;
   }
      
   //impostor fail
   : if (impostor_try == 0) {
      : clear_screen ;
      : print "<'I am sorry<5>> {name} <. We have drawn too much suspicion to ourselves. The impostor would have their guard up by now. Thank you for trying anyway <5>>." ;
      : gosub "end_game2" ;
   }
}

      : press_any_key ;
      
   }

   
   
   
   //walk any other direction

         : print "It's too dark to go that way." ;
